# GitHub Personal Access Token (OPTIONAL but RECOMMENDED)
# Without token: 60 requests/hour rate limit
# With token: 5000 requests/hour rate limit
#
# How to generate:
# 1. GitHub → Settings → Developer settings → Personal access tokens
# 2. Generate new token (classic)
# 3. Select scope: public_repo (for public repository)
# 4. Copy token and paste below
#
# GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_your_github_token_here

# Uncomment and add your token after generating it:
# GITHUB_TOKEN=
